item.title: The Reluctant Entertainers
item.description: Ed Asner: Some of us love to entertain Jorja Fox: But animals don’t get a choice. Eric Roberts: Can you imagine? Mindy Sterling: Can you imagine? Eric Szmanda: Can you imagine? Moby: Being stuck in a metal box. Alexandra Paul: Seeing the world through bars. Tonya Kay: No grass beneath your feet. James Cromwell: No space to run. Eric Szmanda: Tied up. Chained. James Cromwell: Barely able to move. Eric Roberts: Shouted at.
